BOC WatchGuard Policy XML checker utility.

==============================================

    Usage: 
    ./xmlcheck.php args|commands

    -h, --help              this help file
    -i, --infile filename   inputfile filename
    -v, --verbose           verbose output
    --unused                show only unused aliases, if --listaliases

    commands:
    -a aliasname,
      --alias aliasname     print alias aliasname
    -l, --listaliases       lists all aliases
    -p, --listpolicies      lists all policies


==============================================
    
Prerequisites: composer

Setup:

	~/xmlcheck$ composer install

	[...]
	Loading composer repositories with package information
	Updating dependencies (including require-dev)
	Nothing to install or update
	Generating autoload files

	~/xmlcheck$ 


